{
  "name": "XmlNamespace",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlNamespace/XmlNamespace .htm#XmlNamespace.Prefix\">Prefix</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>XmlNamespace</strong> 对象的前缀。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlNamespace/XmlNamespace .htm#XmlNamespace.Uri\">Uri</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>XmlNamespace</strong> 对象的“统一资源标识符”(URI)。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中第一项XML命名空间的前缀和Uri。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> xmlns = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlNamespaces</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第一项XML命名空间的前缀为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlns.Prefix}</span>，Uri为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlns.Uri}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一个工作簿中每项XML命名空间的前缀和Uri。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> namespaces = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlNamespaces</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= namespaces.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlns = namespaces.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${i}</span>项XML命名空间的前缀为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlns.Prefix}</span>，Uri为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlns.Uri}</span>`</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表已添加到工作簿的命名空间。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Prefix",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 类型的数值，该数值表示指定的 XML 命名空间 （命名空间：一种唯一限定元素名称与关系的方法，以避免具有同一名称但来自多个来源的元素发生名称冲突。）的前缀。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中第一项XML命名空间的前缀。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> xmlns = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlNamespaces</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第一项XML命名空间的前缀为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlns.Prefix}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一项XmlMap的根元素命名空间的前缀赋值到A5单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlns = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RootElementNamespace</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = xmlns.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Prefix</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Uri",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 类型的数值，该数值表示指定 XML 命名空间 （命名空间：一种唯一限定元素名称与关系的方法，以避免具有同一名称但来自多个来源的元素发生名称冲突。）的统一资源标识符 (URI) （统一资源标识符 (URI)：通过类型和位置标识 Internet 上资源的字符串。）。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作簿中第二项XML命名空间的Uri。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> xmlns = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlNamespaces</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第二项XML命名空间的Uri为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlns.Uri}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一项XmlMap的根元素命名空间的前缀和Uri分别赋值到A5和A6单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlns = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RootElementNamespace</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = xmlns.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Prefix</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = xmlns.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Uri</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}